window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jake has finally succeeded in destroying two prongs of the Unholy Trio. Now, all that’s left is public enemy number one: Beelzebub.&nbsp;</p> <p>The Lord of Flies won’t concede the Eighth Circle without a fight, though, so Jake has to find a way to power up, and fast.&nbsp;</p> <p>The answer? Hellfire. More specifically, the black Hellfire of fear.&nbsp;</p> <p>But to learn about black Hellfire, Jacob will have to venture into the Shadow World.&nbsp;</p>"; 
